data.system_settings: iPhone 8 Plus - iOS 11.4.1, iPad Air 2 - iOS 12 Public Beta 3
data.actual_result: It opens the image in your selected browser. If you have a title link for the embed, it opens this link.
data.expected_result: Clicking on the thumbnail should always open the image preview of it.
data.short_description: Thumbnails from rich embeds get opened in your browser when clicking on them
data.steps_to_repro: - Create an rich embed with a bot or webhook - Add a thumbnail to it - Try it with and without title link - Click on the thumbnail with your iOS device
